{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/notes/blurb-book-quality-printing/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"The quality of my first Blurb book is great","date":"2009-01-25T00:00:00.000Z","date_pretty":"January 25th, 2009","date_from_now":"11 years ago","last_modified_at":"2018-02-09T14:04:18.000Z","last_modified_at_from_now":"2 years ago","path":"/notes/blurb-book-quality-printing/","author":null,"excerpt":"Using Blurb's BookSmart software was painless and having it printed was equally enjoyable.","tags":["design","review"],"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":1.9927536231884058,"src":"/static/285f07e2e61f63a6d477eec6ba61a0eb/fc20c/blurb-book-featured.jpg","srcSet":"/static/285f07e2e61f63a6d477eec6ba61a0eb/6e883/blurb-book-featured.jpg 275w,\n/static/285f07e2e61f63a6d477eec6ba61a0eb/a09ef/blurb-book-featured.jpg 550w,\n/static/285f07e2e61f63a6d477eec6ba61a0eb/fc20c/blurb-book-featured.jpg 1100w,\n/static/285f07e2e61f63a6d477eec6ba61a0eb/356ef/blurb-book-featured.jpg 1280w","sizes":"(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px"},"fixed":{"src":"/static/285f07e2e61f63a6d477eec6ba61a0eb/fc20c/blurb-book-featured.jpg","height":550,"width":1100}}},"toc":true,"comments":null,"comments_locked":null,"hide_meta":null},"id":"8ba7f834-7bcb-5322-b26e-4185f87a6ba1","html":"<p>Designing a book with Blurb was painless and having it printed was equally enjoyable. I’m really happy with how my first photography book turned out.</p>\n<h2 id=\"options-to-satisfy\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#options-to-satisfy\" aria-label=\"options to satisfy permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Options to satisfy</h2>\n<p>I sprung for the more expensive satin paper to give the pages a nice texture and thickness to them. Next time I’m definitely paying extra for a hardcover with slip so pages are better protected. The only negative I’ve found with the printing is that some of my photographs printed a tad on the dark side. I didn’t bother calibrating my monitor or using any of Blurb’s supplied <a href=\"http://www.blurb.com/downloads/Blurb_ICC_Profile.icc\">ICC color profiles</a>, so that was probably the issue.</p>\n<p>They offer some guidance on <a href=\"http://www.blurb.com/color-management\">color management</a>, that I’ll look at more closely next time. I’m also planning on designing my next book using Adobe InDesign and <a href=\"http://www.blurb.com/indesign-plugin\">Blurb’s Plug-in</a> instead of their <a href=\"http://www.blurb.com/booksmart\">BookSmart<sup>®</sup></a> application — just so I have total control over each page.</p>\n<h2 id=\"sample-pages\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#sample-pages\" aria-label=\"sample pages permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Sample pages</h2>\n<p>Detail photographs of a printed book.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background-color: var(--input-background